OL,3,CWhat is Scotland's 'not proven'
OL,4,Cverdict and why could it be scrapped?
OL,6,FKate Wallace, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FVictim Support Scotland, said: "The
OL,8,Fnot proven verdict is a relic of
OL,9,FScottish criminal law that has
OL,10,Fconfused juries and denied justice to
OL,11,Fvictims for far too long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
