OL,6,FWhat happened to Grace Handling?
OL,8,FGrace Handling was 13 years old when
OL,9,Fshe died after taking an ecstasy
OL,10,Ftablet in 2018 at Callum Owens' house
OL,11,Fin Irvine, Ayrshire.
OL,13,FThe then 17-year-old Owens admitted to
OL,14,Fgiving the drug to the schoolgirl, but
OL,15,Fhe denied culpable homicide, and a
OL,16,Fmajority jury found the charge not
OL,17,Fproven.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
