OL,3,CWhat is Scotland's 'not proven'
OL,4,Cverdict and why could it be scrapped?
OL,6,FGrace's family had to watch Owens walk
OL,7,Ffree from court, and they have
OL,8,Fcampaigned for reform of the justice
OL,9,Fsystem ever since.
OL,11,FHer father, Stewart Handling, says the
OL,12,Ffamily have been denied justice
OL,13,Fbecause of this verdict.
OL,15,F"She was just a wee girl," he told ITV
OL,16,FNews.
OL,18,F"Justice is the missing link in the
OL,19,Fwhole jigsaw."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
