OL,11,FCould not proven soon be scrapped?
OL,13,FThe Scottish Parliament is planning to
OL,14,Fhold a vote that could see the third
OL,15,Fverdict abolished.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Justice Secretary, Angela
OL,18,FConstance, says the Victims Bill is
OL,19,Flandmark legislation, and the
OL,20,Fabolition of the verdict will happen
OL,21,Fquickly if it is voted through.
