OL,3,CWhat is Scotland's 'not proven'
OL,4,Cverdict and why could it be scrapped?
OL,6,FBut amid the calls for reform and
OL,7,Fmodernisation, there are concerns from
OL,8,Fmany lawyers about tinkering with the
OL,9,Fpillars of a centuries-old legal
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FCallum Anderson of Levy & McRae
OL,13,Fsolicitors is among those unconvinced
OL,14,Fthat its removal will help victims or
OL,15,Fcomplainers.
